'''阿拉伯半島'''({{IPAc-en|ə|ˈ|r|eɪ|b|i|ə}}; {{lang-ar|شِبْهُ الْجَزِيرَةِ الْعَرَبِيَّة}}, {{transl|ar|ALA|shibhu l-jazīrati l-ʿarabiyyah}}, “阿拉伯半岛”或 {{lang|ar|جَزِيرَةُ الْعَرَب}}, {{transl|ar|ALA|jazīratu l-ʿarab}}，意为“阿拉伯人的岛”)<ref>{{cite web|title=Arabia {{!}} peninsula, Asia|url=https://www.britannica.com/place/Arabia-peninsula-Asia|website=Encyclopedia Britannica|language=en|access-date=2020-06-22|archive-date=2015-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150503192028/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/31551/Arabia|dead-url=no}}</ref>位於[[西亞|西亞]]，其西邊和[[非洲|非洲]]接壤，它從[[中東|中東]]向東南方伸入[[印度洋|印度洋]]。面積{{convert|3237500|sqkm|abbr=on}}，是世界上最大的[[半島|半島]]<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/peninsulas0000nize|page=[https://archive.org/details/peninsulas0000nize/page/19 19]|title=Peninsulas|last=Niz|first=Ellen Sturm|date=2006-04-10|publisher=Capstone|isbn=9780736861427|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DJgnebGbAB8C&pg=PA710&dq=#v=onepage|title=Encyclopedia of World Geography|last=McColl|first=R. W.|date=2014-05-14|publisher=Infobase Publishing|isbn=9780816072293|language=en|access-date=2020-06-22|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317052744/https://books.google.com/books?id=DJgnebGbAB8C&pg=PA710&dq=#v=onepage|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lazWAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA62&dq=#v=onepage|title=Encyclopedia of National Dress: Traditional Clothing Around the World [2 Volumes]|last=Condra|first=Jill|date=2013-04-09|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=9780313376375|language=en|access-date=2020-06-22|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317052745/https://books.google.com/books?id=lazWAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA62&dq=#v=onepage|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=j47rDQAAQBAJ&pg=PT62&dq=#v=onepage|title=The Everything Understanding Islam Book: A Complete and Easy to Read Guide to Muslim Beliefs, Practices, Traditions, and Culture|last=Dodge|first=Christine Huda|date=2003-04-01|publisher=Simon and Schuster|isbn=9781605505459|language=en|access-date=2020-06-22|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317051848/https://books.google.com/books?id=j47rDQAAQBAJ&pg=PT62&dq=#v=onepage|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.worldatlas.com/articles/15-largest-peninsulas-in-the-world.html|title=15 Largest Peninsulas in the World|work=WorldAtlas|access-date=2017-10-21|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317051902/https://www.worldatlas.com/articles/15-largest-peninsulas-in-the-world.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。向西它與非洲的邊界是[[蘇伊士運河|蘇伊士運河]]、[[紅海|紅海]]和[[曼德海峡|曼德海峽]]。向南它伸入[[阿拉伯海|阿拉伯海]]和[[印度洋|印度洋]]。向東它與[[伊朗|伊朗]]隔[[波斯灣|波斯灣]]和[[阿曼灣|阿曼灣]]相望。[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]、[[葉門|葉門]]、[[阿曼|阿曼]]、[[阿拉伯聯合酋長國|阿拉伯聯合酋長國]]位於阿拉伯半島上。其中以[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]的面積最大，佔據大部分的阿拉伯半島。

阿拉伯半島常年受[[副高壓帶|副高壓帶]]及[[信風帶|信風帶]]控制，非常乾燥，幾乎整個半島都是[[熱帶沙漠氣候|熱帶沙漠氣候]]區並有面積較大的[[無流區|無流區]]，缺乏天然淡水資源，本區有七個沒有河流的國家。半島沿[[波斯灣|波斯灣]]周圍有大量[[石油|石油]]儲藏，自從20世紀陸續成功開採後，給阿拉伯半島上臨[[波斯灣|波斯灣]]的國家帶來了巨大的財富。

阿拉伯半島是[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]的誕生地。伊斯蘭教的創教人[[穆罕默德|穆罕默德]]在這裡出生和生活。半島上的[[麥加|麥加]]是伊斯蘭教的聖地。以阿拉伯半島為中心的[[阿拉伯帝國|阿拉伯帝國]]曾橫跨[[歐亞非大陸|歐亞非大陸]]。今天半島上所有國家都以伊斯蘭教為[[國教|國教]]，並以[[遜尼派|遜尼派]]佔多數。

